---
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Scheduleconsultatioin from '../components/Schedule-consultation.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import Clienttrust from '../components/Clienttrust.astro'
import Testimonial from '../components/Testimonials.astro';
import Popup from "../components/Popup.astro"


import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
	title="Creekside marketing pros" 
  description="Grow your buiness by 100%"
>
	<Nav />
	<section class="relative min-h-dvh flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-primary-900 py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img 
      src="/hero-image.jpg" 
      alt="Creekside Marketing Background" 
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-primary-900/95 via-primary-900/80 to-primary-900/40"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <span class="mb-4 block text-sm/none font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-secondary-300">
        Creekside Marketing Pros
      </span>

      <h1 class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-4xl/tight font-extrabold text-white md:text-6xl/tight lg:text-7xl/tight">
        <span>Stop Wasting Ad Spend.</span>
        <span class="text-secondary-400">Start Growing Revenue.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg/8 text-grey-200 md:text-xl/9">
        Get your free <strong class="text-white">$10K Profit Recovery Audit</strong> and discover the 5-7 hidden leaks draining thousands from your Google and Meta ad accounts. Most take less than 20 minutes to fix.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-8 md:gap-16">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl/none font-bold text-white md:text-4xl/none">$20M+</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm/6 font-medium text-grey-400 uppercase tracking-wide">In Ad Spend Audited</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl/none font-bold text-white md:text-4xl/none">200+</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm/6 font-medium text-grey-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Accounts Audited</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a 
          href="https://calendly.com/creekside_marketing/strategy-call" 
          class="inline-block rounded-sm bg-secondary-500 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-secondary-600 hover:shadow-md hover:translate-y-[-2px] active:scale-95"
        >
          Schedule Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="mb-20 border-l-4 border-grey-200 pl-8">
      <p class="text-xl/8 font-medium text-grey-900 md:text-2xl/9">
        We partner with businesses spending $10k - $100k/month on Meta and Google Ads to 
        <span class="font-extrabold">improve your ROAS by 37% or more within 90 days, or we work for free.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg/7 text-grey-900">
        If your businesses is serious about growth, has a proven offer, and is looking to dominate their competition on Google and/or Meta, Creekside can help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
			<img src="date-range-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="A calander Icon">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          In-depth data analysis
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
          Data-driven optimization ensures efficient spending and better campaign results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
          <img src="bar-chart-02-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="A bar chart with accending lines">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          Campaign & PPC Optimization
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
          Continuous testing and adjustments keep your ads competitive and profitable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
          <img src="spreadsheet-chart-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="Graphic Spreadsheet with line gragh">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          Conversion Tracking
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
          Optimized tracking helps scale winning strategies and eliminate wasted spend
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="aspect-3/4 overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-grey-100 shadow-sm">
              <img 
                src="peterson-rainey.png" 
                alt="Peterson Rainey" 
                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-center">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-900">Peterson Rainey</h4>
              <p class="text-sm/6 font-medium text-grey-600">Co-Founder & Google Ads Expert</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="aspect-3/4 overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-grey-100 shadow-sm">
              <img 
                src="cade-maclean.png" 
                alt="Cade Maclean" 
                class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-center">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-900">Cade Maclean</h4>
              <p class="text-sm/6 font-medium text-grey-600">Co-Founder & Meta Ads Expert</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-secondary-300"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
        <h2 class="text-5xl/none font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary-900 md:text-6xl/none">
          ABOUT <span class="text-secondary-500">US</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 text-base/7 text-grey-700 md:text-lg/8">
          <p>
            At Creekside Marketing, we combine analytical expertise with data-driven marketing to help businesses grow. Founded by longtime friends Cade and Peterson, our agency has been delivering results for over four years.
          </p>
          <p>
            With a background in accounting and an MBA, Cade specializes in Facebook Ads, while Peterson, a mechanical engineer, focuses on Google Ads. Despite earning degrees in highly technical fields, we recognized the need for marketers with a deep understanding of numbers and data.
          </p>
          <p>
            That expertise has made us the people other marketing professionals turn to when they don’t know what to do, and we bring that same level of strategy and precision to every client we work with.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-primary-900">
            Our approach is simple: strategic decision-making, continuous optimization, and custom solutions tailored to your business goals. Let’s grow your business together.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a 
          href="#service" 
          class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-sm bg-secondary-500 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-secondary-600 hover:shadow-md active:scale-95"
        >
          Our Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[url('nnnoise.svg')] py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      
      <h2 class=" text-5xl/none font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary-900 md:text-6xl/none">
        RISK-FREE <span class="text-secondary-500 uppercase">Strategy</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-8 text-center text-base/7 text-grey-800 md:text-lg/8">
        
        <p>
          When you book a consultation call, we're also giving you our $10K Profit Recovery Audit – the exact 247+ point checklist we personally use to find the “hidden leaks” draining 5–6 figures from ad accounts. Most advertisers are hemorrhaging money on 5–7 specific mistakes that take less than 20 minutes total to fix. This audit shows you exactly where to look and what to fix first.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl/9 font-bold text-primary-900">
          (We typically charge $800 to do this type of audit. Yours is free just for showing up to the call. All you have to do is ask for it.)
        </p>

        <p>
          We don't offer magical quick fixes, but long-term, strategic partnerships to position your business to make as much money as possible. While most freelancers optimize for leads, we focus strictly on the revenue we generate for your business, because at the end of the day, who cares how many leads you get if they aren't generating profit? We're who the experts come to when they are stuck and don't know what to do. We’ve cut cost per case in half for law firms, doubled client volume for dental practices, and scaled ecom brands to six-figure months.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-2xl/10 font-extrabold text-primary-900 md:text-3xl/12">
          The biggest risk you can take is not hopping on a call with us to explore how much more your campaigns could achieve.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base/7 text-grey-600">
          Our in-depth knowledge of GA4, Meta Pixel, CAPI, CRM integrations, server-side tracking, CRO, and GTM are all crucial pieces of the puzzle when it comes to enhancing our campaigns' performance. Integrating these platforms into Facebook, Instagram, and Google is critical for success, and we can help you track every data point along your customer journey.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center">
          <a 
            href="https://calendly.com/creekside_marketing/strategy-call" 
            class="rounded-sm bg-secondary-500 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-secondary-600 hover:shadow-md active:scale-95"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Clienttrust />


<section id="service" class="bg-grey-50 py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl/tight font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary-900 md:text-5xl/tight">
