          Facebook Ads (SMM)
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-full bg-grey-200">
          <div class="h-0.5 w-24 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="grow text-base/7 text-grey-600">
          We specialize in using Facebook Ads to drive targeted traffic and maximize ROI for businesses of all sizes. By harnessing audience insights and precise targeting capabilities, we develop tailored campaigns that align with specific business goals, whether it's boosting brand awareness, generating leads, or driving conversions. Our strategy focuses on optimizing ad creatives, placements, and budgets.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="https://creeksidemarketingpros.com/digital-advertising/meta-ads/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm bg-secondary-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white transition-colors hover:bg-secondary-600">
            <svg class="size-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col rounded-sm bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md border-t-4 border-secondary-500 lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary-900 uppercase tracking-tight">
            White Label
          </h3>
          <div class="my-6 flex justify-center">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-64 bg-grey-200 relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 mx-auto h-0.5 w-24 bg-secondary-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base/7 text-grey-600">
            Are you an agency that needs a white-label ad team? We offer full white-label PPC and Social Media Marketing services to make sure your clients are happy. We'll act on behalf of your agency, making the transition seamless from beginning to end, including deliverables, client communication, and ongoing optimizations.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="https://creeksidemarketingpros.com/creekside-marketing-partner-program/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm bg-secondary-500 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white transition-colors hover:bg-secondary-600">
              <svg class="size-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
              Learn More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-primary-900 text-4xl/10 font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl/14">
        Client <span class="text-secondary-500 uppercase">Testimonials</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="hidden mt-4 justify-center gap-1">
        {Array.from({ length: 5 }).map(() => (
          <svg class="size-6 fill-current text-secondary-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
